title: Webmaker Teach the Web Talk: Episode 1 - Privacy
description: For Data Privacy Day we sat down with Stacy Martin, Senior Privacy Manager at Mozilla, to talk about who has access to our data, where it goes or could go, and how we can have a choice in all of it.
